Package eu.h2020.helios_social.core.contextualegonetwork.storage

Class NoStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.h2020.helios_social.core.contextualegonetwork.Storage
      • eu.h2020.helios_social.core.contextualegonetwork.storage.NoStorage
  • public class NoStorage
extends Storage
    This is a Storage implementation that does not perform any actual storage operations. It can be used to facilitate large-scale experiments (e.g. simulations) in dependency modules without evoking disk operations.
    Author:
    Emmanouil Krasanakis (maniospas@iti.gr)
